external_knowledge:
- "Chart the territories of each department" refers to identifying the departments by their names and codes;
- "Financial rivers" is a metaphor for the monetary flow within each department, represented by total and average expenditures;
- "Expenditure streams" refers to the total and average expenditure amounts for each department.

sql:
SELECT d.dept_name, b.description 
FROM departments d
JOIN budget_items b ON d.dept_id = b.dept_id;

